# An Android tachograph app

This is a tachograph appplication for Android devices which has finished developing in 2014.

The application will using Google Map V2 as map implement, which is abandoned and unavailable now. You should refactor it using Google Map v3 if needed.

#Feature:

1. Driving recording
2. Driving path recording and sharing with families(real-time) (server unavialable now)
3. Automatically take pictures when there is a accident(acceleration detection)

# Hope it has some helps and GOOD LUCK
